reviewText: I Want To Be A... Firefightergreat dvd gives you a great insight into being a firefighter

I'm an educator nearing retirement and bought this DVD as a gift. After viewing it, I wanted to become a fireman myself! The presentation is informative and exciting. I have a much greater appreciation for the application process to become a firefighter.  I also appreciated the historical overview of the fire service and purchased another for my personal collection.
